%20and%20I%20took%20many.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20promising%20my%20dad%20I%20wouldn't%20go%20out%20on%20Ipanema%20Beach%20at%20night%2C%20there%20I%20was%20on%20my%20first%20night%20in%20Rio%2C%20dancing%20in%20the%20moonlight%20after%20a%20few%20too%20many%20caipirinhas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20ziplined%20through%20the%20Andes%20in%20Peru%20and%20white%20water%20rafted%20on%20the%20Kananaskis%20River%20in%20Banff%2C%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Vietnam%2C%20I%20hitched%20a%20ride%20from%20Sapa%20down%20a%20mountainside%20on%20the%20back%20of%20a%20motorbike%20with%20some%20random%20guy%20one%20foggy%20evening%2C%20and%20in%20London%2C%20I%20would%20often%20walk%20home%20alone%20in%20the%20early%20hours%20of%20the%20morning%20after%20a%20night%20out.%20Not%20my%20smartest%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20those%20younger%20versions%20of%20myself%20felt%20fearless.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EBecoming%20a%20mom%20made%20me%20stop%20taking%20risks%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20became%20a%20parent%2C%20something%20shifted.%20Some%20primal%20instinct%20kicked%20in%20%E2%80%94%20not%20only%20to%20protect%20my%20child%20but%20also%20to%20survive%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20those%20early%20weeks%20of%20pregnancy%2C%20I%20felt%20like%20some%20sort%20of%20super-smelling%20bloodhound.%20I%20remember%20going%20for%20a%20bike%20ride%20and%20feeling%20like%20I%20could%20smell%20the%20earth%20below%20my%20tires.%20They%20say%20this%20heightened%20sense%20of%20smell%20is%20your%20body's%20way%20of%20protecting%20your%20baby%20against%20external%20threats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecoming%20a%20parent%20awakened%20a%20whole%20new%20world%20of%20instincts%20and%20somewhere%20along%20the%20way%2C%20I%20stopped%20taking%20risks.%20The%20problem%20was%20that%20the%20greatest%20joy%2C%20passion%2C%20and%20thrills%20I%20have%20experienced%20in%20life%20have%20come%20hand-in-hand%20with%20the%20experiences%20that%20have%20terrified%20me%20the%20most.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20signed%20up%20for%20a%20four-day%20hike%20to%20feel%20like%20my%20younger%20self%20again%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20been%20eight%20years%20since%20I%20had%20my%20son%2C%20and%20I%20adore%20my%20family%2C%20but%20I%20felt%20like%20it%20was%20time%20to%20do%20something%20just%20for%20me.%20Something%20that%20reconnects%20me%20to%20those%20younger%20versions%20of%20myself.%20To%20that%20person%20who%20would%20take%20risks%20%E2%80%94%20albeit%20in%20a%20much%20more%20measured%20way%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20decided%20to%20sign%20up%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fbest-fall-hikes-in-the-us-2018-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20four-day%20hike%3C%2Fa%3E%20up%20four%20local%20mountains%20around%20the%20Victorian%20Alps%20near%20where%20I%20live%20in%20the%20town%20of%20Bright%2C%20in%20northeastern%20Victoria%2C%20Australia.%20Not%20an%20easy%20feat%2C%20especially%20for%20a%20mother%20of%20three%20with%20little%20(OK%2C%20let's%20get%20real%2C%20zero)%20training.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20big%20day%20arrived%20and%20my%20alarm%20went%20off%20at%205.30%20am%2C%20I%20felt%20a%20nervous%20sense%20of%20anticipation%20in%20the%20pit%20of%20my%20stomach.%20I%20jumped%20into%20the%20car%20with%20four%20other%20women%20(some%20were%20also%20moms%2C%20like%20me%2C%20who%20are%20looking%20for%20adventure)%20and%20we%20drove%20to%20the%20base%20of%20the%20first%20mountain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%2015%20minutes%20into%20the%20steep%201723m%20hike%20up%20Mount%20Buffalo%2C%20I%20started%20to%20feel%20like%20I've%20made%20a%20terrible%20error%20in%20judgment.%20%26quot%3BHow%20am%20I%20going%20to%20make%20it%20to%20the%20top%3F%26quot%3B%20I%20thought%20to%20myself.%20%26quot%3BIs%20it%20too%20late%20to%20pull%20out%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20views%20from%20Mount%20Buffalo%20on%20day%20one%20of%20the%20author's%20four-day%20hike.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657a0eb77a3c8094d5dcade4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20views%20from%20Mount%20Buffalo%20on%20day%20one%20of%20the%20author's%20four-day%20hike.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EAt%20first%2C%20I%20had%20to%20fight%20the%20urge%20to%20leave%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20fought%20the%20urge%20to%20turn%20around%20and%20drive%20home.%20As%20I%20trudged%20on%2C%20I%20ended%20up%20having%20the%20most%20amazing%20conversations%20with%20other%20women%20on%20the%20trail.%20We%20discussed%20everything%20from%20life%20and%20love%20to%20hobbies%2C%20parenting%2C%20skincare%2C%20and%20aging%20parents.%20After%20around%20three-and-a-half%20hours%2C%20we%20finally%20reached%20the%20top.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20day%20two%2C%20the%20alarm%20went%20off%20again%20at%205%3A30%20am.%20That%20day%20was%20the%20biggest%20mountain%20%E2%80%94%20Victoria's%20second%20highest%20peak%2C%20Mount%20Feathertop%2C%20at%201922m%20elevation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Frage-walking-hiking-self-care-process-emotions-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewalked%20this%20one%20alone%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20deep%20in%20thought.%20When%20I%20finally%20approached%20the%20summit%2C%20my%20fear%20of%20heights%20overwhelmed%20me.%20I%20sat%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20mountain%2C%20about%20100m%20from%20the%20finish%20line%2C%20unable%20to%20move%20as%20panic%20set%20in.%20Although%20I%20couldn't%20quite%20reach%20the%20end%2C%20I%20felt%20a%20sense%20of%20achievement%20that%20I%20had%20come%20this%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20it%20was%20day%20three.%20Muscles%20I%20didn't%20know%20existed%20ached%2C%20but%20I%20kind%20of%20liked%20it.%20I%20felt%20more%20alive%20than%20I%20had%20in%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20mountain%20we%20climbed%20that%20day%2C%20Mount%20Hotham%2C%20proved%20particularly%20challenging.%20The%20trail%20followed%20a%20river%20for%20about%206km%2C%20then%20climbed%20steeply.%20Towards%20the%20end%20was%20the%20hardest%20part.%20Someone%20had%20warned%20me%20about%20%26quot%3Bthe%20wall%26quot%3B%20and%20I%20now%20understood%20why%20they%20called%20it%20that%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%20a%20brutally%20steep%20climb.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20views%20were%20amazing%20and%20I%20was%20glad%20I%20went%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20my%20friend%20and%20I%20finally%20reached%20the%20razorback%2C%20the%20view%20was%20spectacular.%20It%20was%20springtime%20and%20fields%20of%20purple%20and%20yellow%20wildflowers%20danced%20in%20the%20breeze.%20White%20butterflies%20flitted%20around%20us%20as%20we%20neared%20the%20finish%20line.%20I%20felt%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-spending-more-time-outside-is-healthy-2017-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edeep%20sense%20of%20happiness%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20appreciation%20for%20my%20puny%20little%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDay%20four%20was%20a%20winding%20climb%20up%20Mystic%20Hill%20followed%20by%20a%20steep%20descent%20that%20put%20my%2038-year-old%20knees%20to%20the%20test.%20When%20I%20finally%20approached%20the%20finish%20line%2C%20I%20spotted%20my%20husband%20and%20three%20kids%20waiting%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20views%20from%20day%20four%20at%20Mystic%20Hill.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657a0ed50ec98e92f74f232d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20views%20from%20day%20four%20at%20Mystic%20Hill.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20heart%20overflowed%20with%20gratitude%20and%20I%20thought%20about%20the%20lessons%20I%20would%20take%20away%20from%20this%20experience.%20For%20one%2C%20I%20told%20myself%20that%20I%20would%20start%20saying%20'yes'%20to%20things%20that%20challenge%20me%20more%20often.%20And%20I%20won't%20be%20afraid%20to%20step%20outside%20my%20comfort%20zone%20and%20try%20something%20new.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20that's%20where%20the%20magic%20happens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhiking-victorian-alps-fearless-identity-before-parenting-motherhood-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702552681000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657a0e8950edbc52a863ebb5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhiking-victorian-alps-fearless-identity-before-parenting-motherhood-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Before%20I%20became%20a%20mom%2C%20I%20was%20fearless.%20I%20did%20a%204-day%20hike%20in%20the%20Victorian%20Alps%20to%20reconnect%20with%20that%20version%20of%20myself%2C%20and%20I'm%20so%20glad%20I%20did.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Melissa%20Noble)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhiking-victorian-alps-fearless-identity-before-parenting-motherhood-2023-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Krishna%20Janmabhoomi%20Case%3A%20Allahabad%20HC%20Orders%20Survey%20of%20Shahi%20Idgah%20Mosque%20in%20Mathura%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F25112937%2FSEM1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Allahabad%20high%20court%20has%20given%20its%20nod%20for%20the%20survey%20of%20Shahi%20Idgah%20Mosque%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Mathura%20by%20a%20court-appointed%20and%20monitored%20advocate%20commissioner%20in%20response%20to%20petitions%20filed%20by%20Hindutva%20outfits%20which%20claim%20that%20the%20mosque%20stands%20on%20the%20place%20where%20Lord%20Krishna%20was%20born.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20court%20has%20allowed%20our%20plea%20for%20appointment%20of%20a%20commission%20to%20survey%20the%20site.%20More%20details%20will%20be%20out%20when%20the%20order%20is%20uploaded%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fkrishna-janmabhoomi-land-dispute-case-allahabad-hc-survey-of-shahi-idgah-mosque-9068116%2F%5C%22%3Equoted%3C%2Fa%3E%20Ranjana%20Agnihotri%2C%20counsel%20for%20petitioners%2C%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20the%20survey%20of%20Gyanvapi%20mosque%2C%20the%20survey%20of%20the%2017th-century%20mosque%20is%20to%20ascertain%20the%20claims%20being%20made%20by%20Hindutva%20groups%20that%20the%20mosque%20was%20built%20adjacent%20to%20the%20Krishna%20Janmasthal%20(believed%20to%20be%20the%20birthplace%20of%20Lord%20Krishna)%20after%20demolishing%20Katra%20Keshav%20Dev%20Temple.%20The%20temple%20side%20claims%20that%20the%20entire%20tract%20of%20contested%20land%20%E2%80%93%20about%2013.37%20acres%20%E2%80%93%20belongs%20to%20it%20and%20the%20mosque%20should%20be%20removed%20from%20the%20site.%20According%20to%20the%20petitioners%2C%20Katra%20Keshav%20Dev%20Temple%20was%20demolished%20by%20Mughal%20Emperor%20Aurangzeb.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVishnu%20Shankar%20Jain%2C%20another%20advocate%20for%20the%20petitioners%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20court%20has%20allowed%20our%20demand%20that%20an%20advocate%20commissioner%20must%20be%20appointed.%20Who%20will%20be%20the%20advocate%20commissioner%2C%20what%20will%20the%20modalities%20be%2C%20and%20whether%20it%20will%20be%20a%20three-member%20committee%3F%20All%20these%20things%20will%20be%20decided%20on%20December%2018.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20demanded%20that%20in%20the%20Shahi%20Idgah%20mosque%2C%20there%20are%20lots%20of%20signs%20and%20symbols%2C%20and%20to%20know%20the%20actual%20factual%20position%2C%20an%20actual%20advocate%20commissioner%20is%20required.%20The%20court%20has%20allowed%20our%20application.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20total%20of%2018%20separate%20pleas%20were%20filed%20in%20various%20courts%20of%20Mathura%20seeking%20full%20ownership%20of%20the%2013.37-acre%20land%20to%20the%20temple%20management.%20The%20high%20court%20had%20clubbed%20all%20pleas%20and%20transferred%20them%20to%20itself%20for%20adjudicating%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20support%20of%20their%20claims%2C%20these%20groups%20say%20that%20there%20are%20carvings%20of%20lotuses%20on%20some%20walls%20of%20the%20mosque%2C%20as%20well%20as%20shapes%20supposedly%20resembling%20Sheshnag%20%E2%80%93%20the%20snake%20demigod%20in%20Hindu%20mythology.%20This%2C%20they%20say%2C%20proves%20their%20point%20that%20the%20mosque%20was%20indeed%20built%20after%20demolishing%20the%20temple%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-mathuras-krishna-janmabhoomi-land-dispute-court-gives-nod-for-survey-4672258%5C%22%3ENDTV%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mosque%20side%20had%20earlier%20moved%20the%20high%20court%20praying%20for%20the%20quashing%20of%20petitions%20citing%20the%20Places%20of%20Worship%20Act%20of%201991%2C%20which%20maintains%20the%20religious%20status%20of%20any%20place%20of%20worship%20as%20it%20was%20on%20August%2015%2C%201947.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20in%201968%2C%20both%20the%20temple%20side%20(Shri%20Krishna%20Janmasthan%20Seva%20Sansthan)%20and%20the%20mosque%20side%20(Shahi%20Masjid%20Idgah%20Trust)%20inked%20an%20agreement%20to%20the%20effect%20that%2010.9%20acres%20from%20the%20total%2013.37%20acres%20would%20be%20of%20the%20temple%E2%80%99s%20property%20while%202.5%20acres%20would%20belong%20to%20the%20mosque.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Muslim%20side%20is%20expected%20to%20challenge%20the%20high%20court%E2%80%99s%20ruling%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702552516000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F25112937%2FSEM1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fkrishna-ja