es-increases-december-rate-cuts-powell-inflation-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eholding%20interest%20rates%20steady%3C%2Fa%3E%20yet%20again%20in%20its%20final%20major%20decision%20of%20the%20year.%20It%20came%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20more%20data%20reflecting%20cooling%20inflation%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Consumer%20Price%20Index%2C%20which%20measures%20inflation%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finflation-consumer-price-index-november-economic-outlook-fed-interest-rate-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Erose%203.1%25%20year-over-year%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20down%20from%20October's%20reading%20of%203.2%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlongside%20the%20FOMC's%20announcement%2C%20the%20committee%20also%20released%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.federalreserve.gov%2Fmonetarypolicy%2Ffiles%2Ffomcprojtabl20231213.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESummary%20of%20Economic%20Projections%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20outlines%20the%20Fed's%20economic%20outlook%20based%20on%20current%20data.%20The%20committee%20projected%20three%20interest%20rate%20cuts%20in%20the%20coming%20year%2C%20with%20more%20expected%20in%202025%20and%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20cuts%20aren't%20guaranteed%2C%20however%2C%20and%20the%20central%20bank%20is%20still%20watching%20for%20even%20tamer%20inflation.%20%26quot%3BWe%20still%20have%20a%20ways%20to%20go.%20No%20one%20is%20declaring%20victory%2C%20that%20would%20be%20premature%2C%20and%20we%20can't%20be%20guaranteed%20of%20this%20progress.%20So%20we're%20moving%20carefully%20in%20making%20that%20assessment%20of%20whether%20we%20need%20to%20do%20more%20or%20not%2C%26quot%3B%20Fed%20Chair%20Jerome%20Powell%20said%20during%20the%20Wednesday%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ECheaper%20mortgages%20and%20credit%20card%20payments%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Powell%20noted%20that%20the%20interest%20rate%20cut%20projections%20are%20subject%20to%20change%2C%20he%20said%20