m%20apartment%20in%20Portland.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Portland%2C%20she%20was%20paying%20nearly%20%24200%20a%20month%20for%20air%20conditioning%2C%20whereas%20her%201%2C800-square-foot%2C%20three-bedroom%20apartment%20in%20Canton%20is%20%241%2C900%20and%20her%20electricity%20bill%20never%20goes%20above%20%24140.%20Her%20Portland%20apartment%20had%20no%20dishwasher%20and%20no%20washer%20and%20dryer%2C%20while%20she%20has%20all%20those%20amenities%20in%20Georgia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20out%20in%20an%20area%20that%20has%20three%20sides%20of%20my%20complexes%20surrounded%20by%20forest%2C%20and%20the%20other%20side%20is%20the%20main%20road%2C%26quot%3B%20Larson%20said.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20a%20little%20more%20than%20a%20mile%20away%20from%20the%20main%20drag%2C%20which%20has%20an%20AMC%20theater%2C%20has%20all%20the%20major%20chain%20restaurants%20and%20smaller%20ones%2C%20has%20groceries%20and%20craft%20stores%2C%20things%20like%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20chose%20not%20to%20move%20to%20a%20suburb%20that's%20closer%20to%20Atlanta%2C%20like%20Marietta%20or%20Kennesaw%2C%20which%20she%20said%20were%20growing%20fast%20and%20becoming%20more%20expensive.%20She%20knew%20Canton%20was%20becoming%20more%20built%20up%20but%20not%20nearly%20at%20the%20rate%20of%20other%20suburbs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe's%20noticed%20that%20groceries%20are%20a%20bit%20cheaper%20than%20in%20Portland%2C%20and%20gas%20is%20also%20down%20%E2%80%94%20gas%20is%20currently%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgasprices.aaa.com%2F%3Fstate%3DOR%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%244.28%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20gallon%20in%20Portland%2C%20compared%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgasprices.aaa.com%2F%3Fstate%3DGA%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%243.07%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20her%20county.%20The%20quality%20of%20groceries%20she%20said%20is%20slightly%20better%20in%20Georgia%20and%20also%20around%2020%25%20cheaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELarson%20also%20said%20that%20a