om%20(Melia%20Russell)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjack-altman-steps-down-ceo-cofounder-lattice-2023-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2215%20Opposition%20MPs%20Suspended%20From%20Parliament%20For%20Disrupting%20House%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFourteen%20Opposition%20MPs%20have%20been%20suspended%20from%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20one%20from%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20today%20for%20disrupting%20House%20proceedings%2C%20a%20day%20after%20a%20major%20security%20breach%20in%20parliament%20last%20afternoon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%2014%20suspended%20MPs%2C%20nine%20are%20from%20the%20Congress%2C%20two%20from%20the%20CPM%2C%20one%20from%20the%20CPI%2C%20and%20two%20from%20the%20DMK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20MPs%20Manickam%20Tagore%2C%20Md%20Javed%2C%20VK%20Shreekandan%2C%20Benny%20Behanan%2C%20DMK%20MPs%20K%20Kanimozhi%20and%20SR%20Parthiban%2C%20CPM%20MPs%20PR%20Natarajan%20and%20S%20Venkateshan%2C%20and%20CPI%20MP%20K%20Subbarayan%20are%20among%20the%20suspended.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Trinamool%20Congress%20MP%20Derek%20O'Brien%20was%20suspended%20from%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20for%20%26quot%3Bunruly%20behaviour%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20this%20session.%C2%A0However%2C%20he%20refused%20to%20leave%20the%20House%20despite%20being%20suspended%20and%20the%20matter%20has%20been%20sent%20to%20the%20House's%20Privileges%20Committee%20after%20a%20motion%20by%20the%20BJP's%20Piyush%20Goyal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20KC%20Venugopal%20called%20the%20suspension%20a%20%26quot%3Bhorrible%2C%20undemocratic%20move%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20horrible%2C%20undemocratic%20move%20to%20suspend%20opposition%20MPs%20for%20demanding%20an%20answer%20from%20the%20government%20on%20the%20shocking%20security%20breach%20in%20parliament%20yesterday.%20On%20the%20one%20hand%2C%20five%20MPs%20are%20suspended%20for%20demanding%20accountability%2C%20while%20on%20the%20other%2C%20there%20is%20no%20action%20against%20the%20BJP%20MP%20who%20facilitated%20the%20entry%20of%20the%20miscreants.%20This%20is%20a%20murder%20of%20democracy.%20The%20BJP%20government%20has%20reduced%20parliament%20to%20a%20rubber%20stamp.%20Not%20even%20the%20pretence%20of%20a%20democratic%20process%20is%20left%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20the%20day%2C%20Parliamentary%20Affairs%20Minister%20Pralhad%20Joshi%20moved%20a%20resolution%20to%20suspend%20five%20Congress%20MPs%20-%20TN%20Prathapan%2C%20Hibi%20Eden%2C%20Jothimani%2C%20Ramya%20Haridas%2C%20and%20Dean%20Kuriakose%20-%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20session%2C%20reported%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20move%20the%20following%20that%20this%20House%20having%20taken%20misconduct%20of%20TN%20Prathapan%2C%20Hibi%20Eden%2C%20Jothimani%2C%20Ramya%20Haridas%2C%20and%20Dean%20Kuriakose%20Kuryakus%20in%20utter%20disregard%20to%20the%20House%20and%20the%20authority%20of%20this%20Chair%20and%20having%20been%20named%20by%20the%20chair...%20to%20be%20suspended%20from%20the%20service%20of%20the%20House%20for%20reminder%20session%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20resolution%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EB%20Mahtab%20was%20chairing%20the%20proceedings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Lok%20Sabha%20has%20been%20adjourned%20till%2011%20am%20tomorrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParliament%20resumed%20today%20amid%20tensions%20over%20a%20massive%20security%20breach%20a%20day%20earlier%20when%20two%20men%20jumped%20from%20the%20visitors'%20gallery%20into%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20during%20the%20Zero%20Hour%20and%20burst%20smoke%20canisters.%20The%20PM%20was%20not%20in%20Parliament%20yesterday%20since%20he%20was%20attending%20the%20swearing-in%20ceremonies%20of%20the%20BJP's%20two%20new%20chief%20ministers%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Chhattisgarh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20least%20six%20people%20were%20involved%20in%20the%20security%20scare%20inside%20and%20outside%20Parliament%20yesterday.%20Two%20men%20popped%20smoke%20canisters%20inside%20the%20House%2C%20while%20a%20man%20and%20a%20woman%20burst%20them%20outside.%20All%20four%20have%20been%20arrested%2C%20as%20have%20been%20a%20man%20and%20his%20wife%20for%20sheltering%20them%20at%20their%20Gurgaon%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20four%20inside%20have%20been%20identified%20as%20Sagar%20Sharma%2C%20D%20Manoranjan%2C%20Neelam%20Devi%2C%20and%20Amol%20Shinde%2C%20while%20the%20Gurgaon%20man%20has%20been%20identified%20as%20Vicky%20Sharma.%20A%20sixth%20man%20is%20on%20the%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20four%20who%20deployed%20smoke%20canisters%20have%20been%20charged%20under%20the%20stringent%20anti-terror%20law%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%20in%20addition%20to%20relevant%20Sections%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code.%20The%20six%20currently%20in%20custody%2C%20including%20the%20wife%20of%20Vicky%20Sharma%2C%20are%20being%20interrogated%20by%20Delhi%20Police's%20anti-terror%20cell.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20scare%20forced%20authorities%20to%20tighten%20security%20measures%20in%20the%20new%20parliament%2C%20including%20temporarily%20banning%20visitors%20and%20restricting%20non-essential%20personnel%2C%20including%20the%20media.%20Seven%20Lok%20Sabha%20staff%20have%20also%20been%20suspended%20following%20the%20breach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20is%20up%20in%20arms%20over%20the%20incident%20and%20has%20demanded%20a%20probe%20into%20BJP%20MP%20Prathap%20Simha%20since%20the%20visitors'%20passes%20were%20issued%20to%20the%20intruders%20after%20a%20request%20from%20Mr%20Simha's%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYesterday's%20breach%20coincided%20with%20the%2022nd%20anniversary%20of%20the%20terror%20strike%20on%20the%20old%20Parliament%20building%2C%20in%20which%20two%20Pakistan-based%20groups%20attacked%20and%20killed%20nine%20people%2C%20including%20eight%20security%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A17025