e%20Australia%20cricket%20team%2C%20said%20that%20the%20disease%20has%20no%20symptoms%20and%20is%20irreversible.%20%26quot%3BMy%20parents%20got%20told%20when%20I%20was%20born%20that%20I%20had%20chronic%20kidney%20disease%2C%20basically%2C%20there's%20no%20symptoms%2C%20it%20was%20just%20picked%20up%20through%20ultra%20sounds%2C%26quot%3B%20Green%20told%20Channel%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChronic%20kidney%20disease%20is%20basically%20a%20progressive%20disease%20of%20your%20kidney's%20health%20function.%20Unfortunately%2C%20mine%20don't%20filter%20the%20blood%20as%20well%20as%20other%20kidneys.%26quot%3B%20The%2024-year-old%20revealed%20that%20his%20kidney%20function%20is%20currently%20at%20about%2060%20per%20cent%2C%20which%20is%20stage%20two%2C%20with%20stage%20five%20needing%20transplant%20or%20dialysis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFortunately%2C%20I'm%20stage%20two%2C%20but%20if%20you%20don't%20look%20after%20them%20enough%2C%20it%20easily%20goes%20back%20down.%20Kidneys%20can't%20get%20better.%20It's%20irreversible.%20So%20any%20way%20you%20can%20find%20to%20slow%20the%20progression%2C%20you%20basically%20try%20and%20do.%26quot%3B%20The%20condition%20was%20detected%20when%20Green's%20mother%20Tarcy%20had%20her%2019-week%20pregnancy%20scan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20time%20it%20was%20unchartered%20territory%20as%20such%2C%20the%20prognosis%20wasn't%20great.%20There%20were%20life%20expectancy%20issues%20that%20he%20might%20not%20expect%20to%20live%20past%2012%20years%20of%20age%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Green's%20father%2C%20Gary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fast-bowling%20all-rounder%2C%20who%20has%20featured%20in%2024%20Tests%2C%2023%20ODIs%20and%20eight%20T20Is%20since%20making%20his%20Australia%20debut%20in%202020%2C%20said%20the%20disease%20also%20affects%20his%20cricketing%20career%20as%20he%20is%20more%20susceptible%20to%20cramps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20got%20to%20keep%20my%20salt%20and%20my%20protein%20quite%20low%2C%20