C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20allegedly%20choking%20his%20girlfriend.%20The%20case%20is%20pending%2C%20Palmer's%20lawyer%20confirmed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20suing%20the%20Amazon%20Labor%20Union%2C%20the%20dissenters%20first%20attempted%20to%20work%20through%20a%20mediator%20to%20resolve%20their%20differences%20with%20Smalls.%20One%20day%20before%20the%20first%20mediation%20session%20was%20scheduled%20to%20begin%2C%20Smalls'%20camp%20pulled%20out%2C%20according%20to%20documents%20included%20in%20the%20lawsuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20clear%20that%20the%20ALU's%20leadership%20must%20be%20re-organized%20and%20re-affirmed%20by%20the%20membership%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20mediator%2C%20Bill%20Fletcher%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.courtlistener.com%2Frecap%2Fgov.uscourts.nyed.500064%2Fgov.uscourts.nyed.500064.21.5.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ewrote%20in%20a%20June%20memo%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20both%20sides%20after%20Smalls%20and%20his%20supporters%20declined%20mediation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20a%20point%20where%20there%20needs%20to%20be%20profound%20internal%20organizing%20to%20develop%20a%20contract%20campaign%20to%20take%20on%20Amazon%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20union's%20president%20appears%20to%20focus%20little%20on%20the%20internal%20situation%20and%20is%20more%20focused%20externally.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChris%20Smalls%20disputed%20characterizations%20of%20himself%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bcelebrity%26quot%3B%20more%20focused%20on%20fame%20when%20reached%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20give%20a%20damn%20about%20Joe%20Biden%20or%20Hollywood%20red%20carpets%20never%20did%2C%26quot%3B%20Smalls%20wrote%20in%20an%20email%20to%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20media%20attention%20way%20before%20the%20union%20was%20a%20thought.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20signed%20a%20book%20deal%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3