ved%20both%20hilarious%20and%20lovely%20comments.%20'Goodbye'%20is%20a%202021%20family%20comedy-drama%20featuring%20Amitabh%20Bachchan%2C%20Rashmika%20Mandanna%2C%20and%20other%20talented%20actors.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fthis-throwback-picture-of-rashmika-mandanna-and-amitabh-bachchan-from-the-sets-of-goodbye-is-all-about-the-smiles%2Farticleshow%2F105990829.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'What's%20the%20Difference%20Between%20an%20Occupation%20and%20a%20Government%3F'%3A%20PDP%20on%20Kashmir%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F04152043%2FScreenshot-2023-06-04-at-3.15.55-PM.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20People%E2%80%99s%20Democratic%20Party%20(PDP)%20has%20issued%20a%20strongly%20worded%20statement%20in%20its%20monthly%20newspaper%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20people%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20are%20increasingly%20being%20treated%20like%20occupied%20rather%20than%20citizens.%20Specifically%2C%20the%20party%20has%20stated%20that%20with%20the%20discovery%20of%20lithium%20reserves%20in%20Kashmir%2C%20%E2%80%9Ca%20feeling%20of%20doom%20has%20gripped%20the%20region%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20Indian%20companies%20gear%20up%20to%20bid%20for%20the%20treasure%20trove%20of%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20lithium%20mines%2C%20a%20feeling%20of%20doom%20has%20gripped%20the%20region.%20If%20mining%20contracts%20are%20given%20to%20outsiders%2C%20limitless%20mining%20will%20inevitably%20damage%20the%20ecology%20and%20economy%2C%20but%20not%20before%20displacing%20local%20populations.%20The%20extraction%20of%20lithium%20not%20only%20contaminates%20fresh%20water%20sources%2C%20but%20its%20harmful%20toxins%20also%20leach%20into%20fertile%20lands%2C%20making%20them%20unsuitable%20for%20agriculture.%20And%20after%20causing%20all%20this%20damage%2C%20the%20economic%20benefits%20will%20go%20to%20outsiders%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20party%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20comes%20soon%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20decision%20that%20ruled%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20reading%20down%20of%20Article%20370%20as%20constitutionally%20valid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERead%20the%20full%20text%20of%20the%20statement%20below.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20the%20difference%20between%20an%20occupation%20and%20a%20government%3F%20Current%20events%20around%20the%20world%20have%20brought%20this%20issue%20to%20the%20forefront%2C%20and%20the%20answer%20is%20rather%20simple.%20Before%20we%20delve%20into%20that%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20given%20the%20final%20verdict%20on%20Article%20370%2C%20and%20once%20again%2C%20Kashmir%20is%20grieving.%20To%20quote%20Arab%20poet%20Ansar%20Yawar%2C%20%E2%80%9Cexpecting%20a%20solution%20from%20those%20who%20created%20the%20web%20is%20like%20a%20bug%20asking%20the%20spider%20for%20its%20freedom%2C%20not%20realizing%20the%20purpose%20of%20the%20web.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20bright%20sunny%20day%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20HM%20Amit%20Shah%20found%20himself%20mourning%20the%20loss%20of%20Pakistan-occupied%20Kashmir.%20Instead%20of%20ruminating%20over%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cblunders%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20BJP%20needs%20to%20ask%20themselves%20what%20they%20have%20done%20for%20the%20Indian%20Kashmir%20since%20they%20came%20to%20power%20in%202014.%20Other%20than%20dividing%20up%20our%20land%20and%20resources%20for%20their%20cronies%20and%20using%20their%20brute%20majority%20in%20Parliament%20to%20airdrop%20laws%20to%20disempower%20our%20people%2C%20what%20has%20BJP%20done%20for%20us%3F%20Perhaps%20they%20regret%20losing%20Pakistan-occupied%20Kashmir%20because%20they%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20treat%20it%20like%20the%20spoils%20of%20war.%20A%20quick%20lesson%20in%20history%20would%20tell%20them%20that%20it%20is%20because%20of%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20that%20Kashmir%20acceded%20to%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20winter%20of%202023%2C%20Kashmir%20has%20been%20facing%20the%20worst%20power%20cuts%20in%20more%20than%2020%20years.%20Despite%20the%20installation%20of%20smart%20meters%2C%20most%20Kashmiri%20homes%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20electricity%20for%20more%20than%20a%20few%20hours%20per%20day.%20Even%20hospitals%20have%20not%20been%20spared.%20Kashmir%20needed%20S00%20MW%20of%20power%20to%20meet%20the%20current%20curtailment%20schedule%20of%208.5%20hours%20and%204.5%20hours%20for%20non-metered%20and%20metered%20areas%2C%20respectively.%20After%20begging%20GOI%2C%20we%20were%20given%20293%20MW%2C%20of%20which%2080%20MW%20was%20given%20to%20Ladakh.%20That%20us%20with%20less%20than%20balf%20of%20what%20we%20needed.%20J%26amp%3BK%20has%2021%20power%20projects%20that%20could%20not%20only%20meet%20our%20needs%20but%20generate%20a%20surplus%20of%20900%20MW%2C%20but%20because%20of%20the%20disproportionate%20power%20sharing%20agreement%2C%20we%20receive%20less%20than%20half%20of%20the%20power%20we%20generate.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20we%20purchased%20power%20from%20the%20Northern%20Grid%2C%20but%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20local%20government%2C%20GOI%20has%20failed%20to%20do%20the%20same.%20It%E2%80%99s%20laughable%20that%20BJP%20expects%20the%20world%20to%20believe%2080%20percent%20of%20Kashmiris%20want%20to%20continue%20living%20like%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Indian%20companies%20gear%20up%20to%20bid%20for%20the%20treasure%20trove%20of%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20lithium%20mines%2C%20a%20feeling%20of%20doom%20has%20gripped%20the%20region.%20If%20mining%20contracts%20are%20given%20to%20outsiders%2C%20limitless%20mining%20will%20inevitably%20damage%20the%20ecology%20and%20economy%2C%20but%20not%20before%20displacing%20local%20populations.%20The%20extraction%20of%20lithium%20not%20only%20contaminates%20fre