3E%3Cp%3EThis%20left%20me%20doubting%20my%20decision%20to%20leave%20my%20fianc%C3%A9%20and%20our%20Connecticut%20home%20behind%20and%20head%20overseas%20to%20Germany.%20I%20also%20didn't%20speak%20German.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20despite%20my%20misgivings%2C%20I%20flew%20to%20Hamburg%20for%20a%20weeklong%20seafarer%20training%20for%20new%20crew%20members%20in%20June%202022.%20This%20was%20a%20requirement%20before%20I%20was%20allowed%20to%20set%20sail%20on%20what%20would%20be%20my%20new%20home%20for%20nearly%20five%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20I%20got%20the%20job%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224864%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20woman%20performing%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6579ea050ec98e92f74f0b71%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223648%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESheffy%20performing.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Autumn%20Eliza%20Sheffy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20spring%2C%20performers%20from%20all%20over%20the%20world%20audition%20for%20a%20spot%20as%20an%20entertainer%20aboard%20one%20of%20AIDA's%2013%20passenger%20ships.%20My%20audition%20was%20in%20New%20York%20City.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20performed%20two%20songs%20and%20a%20one-minute%20dance%20and%20returned%20two%20days%20later%20to%20sing%20two%20more%20songs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20day%20after%20my%20callback%2C%20my%20phone%20rang%2C%20and%20I%20got%20a%20job%20offer%20%E2%80%94%20with%20a%20slight%20twist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20a%20standard%20six-month%20contract%2C%20my%20offer%20was%20to%20replace%20a%20performer%20who'd%20gotten%20sick%20and%20whose%20contract%20got%20cut%20short.%20The%20cast%20had%20already%20been%20performing%20together%20for%20almost%20a%20month%20and%20a%20half%2C%20so%20I'd%20have%20to%20learn%20everything%20on%20my%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20the%20thought%20of%20playing%20catch-up%20was%20pretty%20daunting%2C%20but%20I%20accepted%20the%20position%20and%20two%20weeks%20later%2C%20I%20made%20my%20way%20to%20the%20MTC%20Marine%20Training%20Center%20Hamburg%20GmbH.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20training%20was%20comprehensive%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20practiced%20maneuvers%2C%20including%20climbing%20down%20the%20side%20of%20a%20ship%20in%20case%20of%20an%20emergency.%20There's%20also%20an%20indoor%20pool%20where%20we%20learned%20how%20to%20float%2C%20get%20inside%20a%20raft%2C%20and%20safely%20connect%20people%20in%20the%20event%20of%20a%20water%20evacuation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcruise-liner-launch-msc-explora-delayed-faulty-fire-panels-report-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFire%20is%20a%20major%20concern%20on%20cruise%20ships%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20so%20knowing%20what%20to%20do%20in%20these%20instances%20is%20crucial%2C%20considering%20no%20firefighters%20are%20on%20board.%20There%20are%20no%20police%20officers%20on%20the%20ship%20either%2C%20but%20there%20are%20security%20personnel%20who%20typically%20have%20law-enforcement%20or%20military%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20emergencies%2C%20we're%20the%20ones%20responsible%2C%20which%20is%20why%20all%20crew%20must%20undergo%20this%20training.%20Then%2C%20once%20they%20begin%20working%20on%20the%20ship%2C%20all%20crew%20members%20must%20do%20weekly%20safety%20drills%20for%20up%20to%20two%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELuckily%2C%20there%20were%20no%20emergencies%20while%20I%20was%20on%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EPacking%20the%20essentials%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcruise-ships-with-nicest-cabins-cruisecritic-2019-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOur%20cabins%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20essentially%20metal%20boxes%2C%20so%20magnets%20come%20in%20especially%20handy%20because%20you%20hang%20everything%20in%20your%20room%20from%20clothing%20to%20towels%20to%20photos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20packed%20a%20hard%20drive%20full%20of%20downloaded%20movies%20and%20TV%20shows%2C%20my%20acoustic%20guitar%2C%20a%20chord%20book%20since%20I'm%20still%20learning%20to%20play%2C%20my%20iPad%20filled%20with%20books%2C%20a%20camera%2C%20tarot%20cards%2C%20coloring%20books%2C%20and%20pencils%2C%20which%20come%20in%20handy%20during%20long%20days%20at%20sea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20brought%20a%20hanging%20shoe%20organizer%20to%20store%20sunglasses%2C%20face%20masks%2C%20letters%20from%20loved%20ones%2C%20and%20extra%20USB%20drives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20tends%20to%20be%20very%20dry%20on%20ships%2C%20which%20is%20not%20ideal%20for%20singers%2C%20but%20humidifiers%20are%20a%20fire%20hazard.%20Instead%2C%20I%20came%20prepared%20with%20throat-coat%20tea%2C%20my%20tea%20mug%2C%20and%20lots%20of%20cough%20drops.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20cabin%20was%20reminiscent%20of%20Harry%20Potter's%20living%20quarters%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fhow-to-live-work-remote-on-cruise-ship-full-time-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELiving%20inside%20a%20small%20interior%20cabin%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20no%20window%20felt%20like%20living%20inside%20a%20shipping%20container%2C%20but%20it's%20also%20oddly%20cozy.%20There's%20no%20sense%20of%20time.%20Normally%2C%20I'm%20claustrophobic%2C%20but%20I%20got%20used%20to%20it%20pretty%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20lots%20of%20crew%20members%20live%20in%20shared%20quarters%2C%20often%20with%20bunk%20beds%2C%20I%20was%20fortunate%20enough%20to%20have%20a%20single%20cabin%20and%20only%20have%20to%20share%20a%20bathroom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20only%20saw%20my%20fianc%C3%A9%20once%20in%205%20months%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20my%20time%20at%20sea%2C%20I%20only%20saw%20my%20fianc%C3%A9%20%E2%80%94%20now%20husband%20%E2%80%94%20when%20he%20joined%20me%20for%20a%20four-day%20cruise%20to%20celebrate%20his%2030th%20birthday.%20Being%20apart%20for%20that%20long%20might%20not%20work%20for%20many%20couples%2C%20but%20he's%20a%20touring%20musician%2C%20so%20we're%20used%20to%20spending%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20away%20from%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20crew%20WiFi%20on%20board%2C%20but%20FaceTime%20didn't%20work%20while%20the%20ship%20was%20moving%2C%20so%20while%20at%20sea%2C%20I%20relied%20on%20WhatsApp%20to%20communicate%20with%20friends%20and%20family.%20I%20used%20FaceTime%20while%20at%20ports.%20Occasionally%2C%20our%20WiFi%20would%20go%20down%2C%20and%20I%20couldn't%20contact%20anyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPerforming%20on%20a%20different%20level%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPerforming%20can%20be%20hard%20work%2C%20but%20performing%20on%20a%20stage%20in%20high%20heels%20during%20rough%20seas%20takes%20it%20to%20a%20new%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20me%2012%20days%20to%20learn%20all%20the%20shows.%20I%20prepared%20by%20memorizing%20all%20of%20the%20music%20and%20watching%20the%20shows%20on%20YouTube%20before%20boarding%20the%20ship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECOVID-19%20was%20still%20prevalent%2C%20which%20meant%20performers%20constantly%20dropped%20in%20and%20out%20of%20shows%20and%20needed%20to%20quarantine.%20This%20led%20to%20us%20having%20to%20make%20last-minute%20show%20changes%20based%20on%20who%20was%20available.%20Sometimes%20that%20meant%20learning%20roles%20an%20hour%20before%20we%20took%20the%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20night%20we%20did%20two%20back-to-back%20shows.%20We%20had%20four%20different%20shows%20in%20rotation%20and%20a%20finale%20and%20never%20repeated%20the%20same%20show%20twice%20during%20a%20trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20I%20did%20when%20I%20wasn't%20working%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20woman%20standing%20in%20front%20of%20a%20cruise%20ship%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6579e9c50ec98e92f74f0b52%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESheffy%20and%20the%20ship.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Autumn%20Eliza%20Sheffy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3