Cunfortunate%E2%80%9D%20and%20called%20for%20all%20parliamentarians%20to%20exercise%20caution%20in%20issuing%20passes%20while%20opposition%20MPs%20moved%20to%20the%20well%20of%20the%20house%20chanting%20slogans%20of%20%E2%80%9Cshame%2C%20shame%E2%80%9D%20and%20demanding%20a%20statement%20from%20the%20home%20minister.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20December%2013%2C%20two%20men%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fparliament-security-breach-anniversary-slogan-dictatorship%5C%22%3Ejumped%20from%20the%20public%20gallery%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20hall%20and%20opened%20smoke%20canisters%2C%20causing%20House%20proceedings%20to%20be%20interrupted.%20The%20security%20breach%20occurred%20on%20the%20anniversary%20of%20the%202001%20attack%20on%20the%20parliament%2C%20then%20housed%20in%20a%20different%20building.%20The%20two%20who%20entered%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20had%20received%20their%20entry%20passes%20from%20BJP%20MP%20Pratap%20Simha%20and%20shouted%20slogans%20but%20did%20not%20attempt%20to%20harm%20anyone%20in%20the%20hall.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmid%20protests%20from%20opposition%20MPs%2C%20Singh%20rose%20from%20his%20chair%20and%20said%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20incident%20is%20quite%20unfortunate%2C%20there%20is%20no%20doubt%20about%20it.%20You%20(speaker)%20took%20immediate%20note%20of%20the%20incident%20and%20ordered%20a%20probe.%20I%20believe%20that%20all%20MPs%20both%20from%20the%20opposition%20and%20the%20government%20need%20to%20maintain%20caution.%20So%20that%20passes%20are%20not%20issued%20to%20people%20who%20then%20go%20ahead%20and%20spread%20anarchy%20in%20the%20house.%20You%20have%20already%20ordered%20a%20probe%20and%20other%20precautionary%20measures%20that%20can%20be%20taken%20in%20the%20future%20will%20be%20done%20as%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmid%20concerns%20raised%20by%20opposition%20MPs%20over%20the%20security%20measures%20in%20the%20new%20parliament%20building%2C%20Singh%20said%20that%20such%20incidents%20had%20also%20taken%20place%20in%20the%20old%20parliament.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20also%20want%20to%20inform%20you%20that%20the%20old%20parliament%20building%20also%20saw%20similar%20incidents%20including%20throwing%20papers%20into%20the%20well%20of%20the%20house%20as%20well%20as%20jumping.%20All%20MPs%20should%20condemn%20the%20incident.%20Since%20a%20probe%20has%20been%20ordered%20and%20future%20measures%20are%20being%20looked%20into%2C%20there%20is%20no%20need%20to%20spread%20anarchic%20conditions%20inside%20the%20house%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Delhi%20police%20have%20arrested%20five%20people%20in%20total%3A%20Sagar%20Sharma%20and%20Manoranjan%20D%2C%20the%20two%20men%20who%20entered%20the%20house%3B%20as%20well%20as%20two%20others%20who%20protested%20outside%20parliament%2C%20identified%20as%20Amol%20Shinde%20and%20Neelam%3B%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20individual%2C%20Vikram%2C%20was%20arrested%20as%20a%20suspected%20accomplice.%20As%20sixth%20person%2C%20Lalit%2C%20was%20on%20the%20run.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDerek%20O%E2%80%99Brien%20suspended%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20on%20Thursday%2C%20opposition%20members%20demanded%20a%20short-term%20discussion%20on%20the%20security%20breach%20the%20day%20before.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERajya%20Sabha%20chair%20and%20vice%20president%20Jagdeep%20Dhankar%20informed%20the%20house%20that%20he%20had%20received%2026%20notices%20%E2%80%93%20including%20from%20leader%20of%20the%20opposition%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20%E2%80%93%20demanding%20suspension%20of%20business%20to%20discuss%20the%20security%20breach%20but%20said%20that%20he%20did%20not%20find%20merit%20in%20the%20notices.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBoth%20houses%20were%20adjourned%20within%20an%20hour%20of%20proceedings%20starting.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20resumed%20proceedings%20at%20noon%2C%20Dhankar%20accused%20TMC%20MP%20O%E2%80%99Brien%20of%20%E2%80%9Cgross%20misconduct%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cgross%20defiance%20of%20the%20directions%20of%20the%20chair.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20was%20suspended%20for%20the%20remainder%20of%20the%20session%20after%20a%20motion%20was%20moved%20by%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20house%20and%20BJP%20MP%20Piyush%20Goyal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGoyal%20said%20that%20the%20house%20%E2%80%9Chaving%20taken%20serious%20note%20of%20the%20misconduct%20of%20Shri%20Derek%20O%E2%80%99Brien%20member%20who%20has%20entered%20the%20well%20of%20the%20house%20and%20has%20been%20continuously%20shouting%20slogans%2C%20gesticulating%20aggressively%20at%20the%20chair%20thereby%20disrupting%20the%20proceedings%20of%20the%20house%20in%20utter%20disregard%20to%20the%20authority%20of%20the%20chair%20and%20having%20been%20named%20by%20the%20chair%E2%80%9D%20be%20suspended.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmid%20sloganeering%20from%20opposition%20members%20after%20O%E2%80%99Brien%E2%80%99s%20suspension%2C%20Dhankar%20adjourned%20the%20proceedings%20till%202%20pm.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEarlier%2C%20opposition%20members%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20also%20held%20a%20meeting%20before%20the%20session%20started%20to%20discuss%20the%20security%20breach.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20parties%20demanded%20a%20detailed%20statement%20by%20Shah%20in%20both%20houses%20of%20parliament%2C%20as%20well%20as%20strict%20action%20against%20the%20BJP%20MP%20Pratap%20Simha%20%E2%80%93%20who%20provided%20the%20visitor%20passes%20to%20the%20intruders.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThe%20INDIA%20parties%20are%20demanding%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1.%20A%20detailed%20statement%20by%20the%20Home%20Minister%20in%20both%20Houses%2C%20followed%20by%20a%20discussion%20on%20the%20very%20serious%20and%20shocking%20security%20breach%20witnessed%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20yesterday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2.%20Strict%20action%20against%20the%20BJP%20MP%20Pratap%20Simha%20who%20provided%20the%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20(%40Jairam_Ramesh)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJairam_Ramesh%2Fstatus%2F1735182565567308169%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2014%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20refusal%20to%20accept%20these%20perfectly%20legitimate%20and%20reasonable%20demands%20has%20led%20to%20the%20adjournment%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20today%20morning%2C%E2%80%9D%20Congress%E2%80%99%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20wrote%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E14%20Lok%20Sabha%20MPs%20suspended%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20proceedings%20resumed%20at%202%20pm%2C%20parliamentary%20affairs%20minister%20Pralhad%20Joshi%20accused%20%E2%80%9Csome%20members%20of%20politicising%E2%80%9D%20the%20issue%2C%20before%20moving%20a%20motion%20to%20suspend%20five%20Congress%20MPs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20while%20he%20agrees%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20unfortunate%20incident%E2%80%9D%20raised%20concerns%20about%20the%20safety%20and%20security%20of%20MPs%2C%20he%20said%20that%20there%20is%20a%20need%20to%20%E2%80%9Cappreciate%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20honourable%20speaker%20promptly%20held%20a%20meeting%20with%20all%20floor%20leaders%20and%20listened%20to%20their%20concerns%20regarding%20the%20security%20of%20the%20parliament%20premises.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSome%20of%20the%20suggestions%20given%20have%20already%20been%20implemented.%20As%20the%20speaker%20observed%20this%20morning%20also%20that%20in%20the%20future%2C%20further%20measures%20will%20be%20taken%20to%20strengthen%20parliament%E2%80%99s%20security.%20In%20my%20opinion%2C%20this%20matter%20concerns%20us%20all%20and%20we%20have%20to%20speak%20in%20one%20voice%20on%20such%20a%20grave%20national%20issue.%20No%20politics%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20done%20by%20anyone%20on%20such%20grave%20issues.%20We%20have%20to%20rise%20above%20politics%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJoshi%20then%20went%20on%20to%20list%20the%20previous%20incidents%20of%20security%20breaches%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20past%20many%20such%20incidents%20have%20taken%20place.%20I%20am%20not%20comparing%20past%20incidents%20and%20defending%20today%E2%80%99s%20incident%20but%20we%20have%20to%20learn%20lessons%20from%20our%20past%20to%20bring%20a%20bright%20future.%20On%20April%2011%2C%201974%2C%20one%20person%20named%20Ratan%20Chandra%20Gupta%20one%20person%20shouted%20slogans%20from%20the%20visitors%E2%80%99%20gallery%20while%20carrying%20two%20pistols.%20In%20July%201974%2C%20Biplab%20Basu%20was%20found%20carrying%20a%20dagger%20hidden%20on%20his%20person%20and%20tried%20to%20enter%20the%20visitors%E2%80%99%20gallery.%20On%20November%2026%2C%201974%2C%20Satyajit%20Singh%20carried%20explosives%20and%20a%20dagger%20hidden%20on%20his%20person%20to%20the%20visitors%E2%80%99%20gallery.%20On%20January%209%20and%2010%2C%201999%2C%20Badri%20Prasad%20and%20Pushpendra%20Chavan%20jumped%20from%20the%20gallery%20to%20the%20chamber%20of%20Lok%20Sabha.%20As%20I%20have%20already%20said%20we%20are%20not%20comparing%20but%20these%20kinds%20of%20unfortunate%20incidents%20have%20been%20happening%20since%20beginning-shouting%20slogans%2C%20throwing%20paper%20and%20jumping%20from%20the%20gallery.%20I%20have%20many%20such%20incidents%20%5Bto%20list%5D.%20We%20all%20understand%20that%20parliament%20is%20for%20protecting%20the%20immunity%20and%20efficient%20discharge%20of%20functions.%20Internal%20security%20is%20under%20the%20speaker.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20such%20matters%20have%20been%20dealt%20with%20by%20directions%20of%20the%20speaker.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20appropriate%20agencies%20would%20be%20dealing%20with%20the%20incident%20as%20per%20the%20law%20of%20the%20land%20and%20that%20the%20speaker%20had%20already%20written%20to%20the%20home%20secretary%20for%20a%20high-level%20enquiry%20which%20has%20already%20been%20initiated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20government%20is%20also%20very%20sensitive%20to%20these%20matters%20so%20I%20urge%20you%20to%20allow%20the%20proceedings%20of%20the%20house%20to%20take%20place.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20added%20that%20it%20has%20become%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20habit%20of%20some%20members%20to%20politicise%20issues.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20moved%20a%20resolution%20to%20suspend%20five%20Congress%20MPs%20T.N.%20Prathapan%2C%20Hibi%20Eden%2C%20S.%20Jothimani%2C%20Ramya%20Haridas%20and%20Dean%20Kuriakose%20for%20%E2%80%9Cutter%20disregard%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20house%20and%20undermining%20the%20authority%20of%20the%20chair.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20house%20resumed%20at%203%20pm%2C%20Joshi%20moved%20a%20resolution%20to%20suspend%20nine%20more%20opposition%20MPs%2C%20including%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20Manickam%20Tagore%2C%20Mohammad%20Jawed%20and%20DMK%E2%80%99s%20Kanimozhi%20and%20S.R.%20Parthiban.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Lok%20Sabha%20was%20then%20adjourned%20for%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENote%3A%20This%20article%20was%20updated%20after%20it%20was%20published.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702547383000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F14145946%2FScreenshot-2023-12-14-at-2.59.04%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fparliament-security-breach-rajnath-singh-opposition-statement-amit-shah%