t%20a%20little%20%E2%80%98I%20told%20you%20so%E2%80%99%20or%20%E2%80%98what%20else%20did%20you%20expect%3F%E2%80%99%20Because%20this%20is%20what%20was%20expected%2C%20nothing%20better%2C%20nothing%20newer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20homes%20were%20not%20chained%20this%20time.%20We%20were%20free%20to%20lodge%20protests.%20Did%20we%20take%20out%20grand%20protests%3F%20We%20did%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20does%20it%20mean%20we%20have%20reconciled%20collectively%3F%20Are%20we%20reconciled%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20we%20no%20longer%20have%20a%20say%20in%20things%20that%20define%20our%20political%20future%3F%20Reconciled%20that%20we%20have%20lost%20our%20voice%20and%20our%20voice%20does%20not%20matter%2C%20that%20we%20have%20no%20representation%20in%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20democracy%3F%20We%20certainly%20have%20reconciled%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20for%20the%20last%20four%20and%20half%20years%2C%20our%20downgraded%20erstwhile%20state%20and%20now%20a%20Union%20territory%20has%20had%20no%20elected%20assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20are%20reconciled%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20last%20elections%20happened%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20nearly%20a%20decade%20ago.%20This%20is%20the%20longest%20ever%20stretch.%20The%20last%20time%20it%20happened%20was%20at%20the%20peak%20of%20militancy%2C%20when%201987%E2%80%99s%20famously%20rigged%20elections%20were%20followed%20in%201996.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20are%20reconciled%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20we%20may%20not%20see%20a%20functional%20democracy%20in%20many%20more%20years%20to%20come.%20We%20are%20reconciled%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20people%20can%20lose%20their%20jobs%20on%20mere%20charges%20of%20abetment%20of%20terrorism%2C%20stone%20pelting%20or%20any%20other%20family%20member%20being%20involved%20%E2%80%93%20even%20though%20the%20charges%20would%20not%20be%20strong%20enough%20to%20try%20them%20in%20courts%20of%20law.%20Social%20media%20posts%20can%20open%20the%20doors%20to%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20are%20reconciled%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20every%20voice%20raised%20is%20%E2%80%98treachery%E2%80%99%2C%20every%20right%20asserted%20is%20%E2%80%98anti-national%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20know%20that%20we%20can%20pray%20for%20people%20of%20Gaza%20in%20our%20hearts%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fjk-authorities-seal-srinagars-jamia-masjid-to-prevent-pro-palestine-protests%5C%22%3Enot%20utter%20a%20word%20on%20the%20same%20in%20gatherings%20and%20mosques%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20know%20that%20our%20mosques%20and%20religious%20places%20can%20be%20locked%20for%20years%20together%2C%20and%20preachers%20barred%20from%20leading%20prayers.%20We%20are%20reconciled%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20every%20few%20months%20there%20will%20be%20an%20amendment%20in%20previous%20laws%20or%20some%20new%20laws%20will%20be%20made%2C%20to%20strip%20us%20of%20our%20millenia-old%20identity%20even%20further.%20These%20include%20the%20domicile%20law%2C%20the%20changed%20land%20ownership%20rules%2C%20delimitation%20of%20electoral%20seats%20which%20takes%20the%20arithmetic%20across%20the%20mountains%2C%20to%20the%20liking%20of%20the%20ruling%20BJP.%20The%20changes%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20administration%20cadre%2C%20jobs%2C%20education%2C%20business%2C%20et%20al.%20We%20have%20seen%20it%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FGVqpNulxkdc%3Fsi%3DHJ3CyGj3dns3Kh35%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20have%20we%20actually%20reconciled%20to%20it%20all%3F%20Have%20we%20given%20up%20or%20have%20we%20surrendered%20the%20right%20to%20dissent%3F%20The%20bad%20news%20is%20we%20have%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20silence%20in%20Kashmir%20is%20loud%20and%20deafening%20and%20its%20people%20are%20isolated.%20Kashmir%20continues%20to%20be%20the%20paradise%20it%20was%2C%20people%20continue%20to%20remain%20the%20best%20hosts%20you%20will%20have%20but%20we%20are%20far%20from%20happy.%20With%20every%20passing%20day%2C%20as%20the%20voices%20in%20Kashmir%20are%20muffled%2C%20we%20are%20stepping%20closer%20and%20closer%20to%20complete%20political%20alienation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20upheld%20the%20reading%20down%20of%20Article%20370%2C%20Kashmir%20remained%20unfazed.%20Its%20people%20believed%20that%20the%20court%20case%20was%20a%20lost%20battle%20from%20the%20word%20go.%20The%20way%20the%20honourable%20courts%20were%20batting%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20government%20during%20the%20hearing%20was%20indicative%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20while%20right-minded%20people%20were%20posting%20on%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20verdict%2C%20Kashmir%20was%20posting%20in%20support%20of%20Palestinian%20women%20and%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20anger%20in%20Kashmir%2C%20but%20there%20may%20be%20hopelessness%20and%20a%20deep%20sense%20of%20political%20alienation%20%E2%80%93%20a%20dangerous%20concoction%20as%20we%20saw%20once%20in%201989.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20now%2C%20with%20the%20treatment%20meted%20out%20to%20the%20very%20torch%20bearers%20of%20the%20Indian%20democracy%20amid%20the%20alienation%2C%20one%20can%20only%20keep%20one%E2%80%99s%20fingers%20crossed%20and%20hope%20that%20the%20neighbours%20would%20remain%20weak%20and%20engrossed%20in%20their%20own%20battles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20reads%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Ffour-important-takeaways-from-the-supreme-court-ruling-on-jammu-and-kashmir%5C%22%3EFour%20Important%20Takeaways%20From%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20Ruling%20on%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKashmiris%20expect%20many%20more%20decisions%20with%20wide%20optics%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20in%20the%20run%20up%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20next%20year.%20And%20with%20a%20unilateral%20decision%20making%20in%20progress%20and%20no%20local%20political%20representation%20to%20fight%20for%20them%2C%20many%20Kashmiris%20believe%20that%20the%20BJP%20ultimately%20wants%20to%20change%20the%20demographic%20character%20of%20the%20erstwhile%20state.%20Kashmiris%20had%20long%20ago%20understood%20that%20they%20are%20just%20a%20poll%20plank%20and%20that%20the%20claims%20of%20%E2%80%98restoring%20normalcy%E2%80%99%20in%20Kashmir%20can%20garner%20votes%20for%20parties%20across%20the%20mainland.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20judgement%20gives%20further%20boost%20to%20the%20political%20rhetoric%20and%20adds%20to%20the%20narrative%20that%20Kashmiris%20have%20been%20shown%20their%20place%E2%80%99%20under%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20tough%20stance%20on%20Kashmir%20and%20the%20revocation%20has%20become%20a%20war%20cry%20in%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country%20too.%20The%20vote%20bank%20which%20the%20party%20appeals%20to%20will%20consider%20the%20verdict%20another%20victory%20in%20national%20interest.%20The%20WhatsApp%20forwards%20will%20now%20further%20cement%20the%20notions%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20has%20managed%20to%20do%20what%20governments%20for%2070%20years%20failed%20to%20do%20%E2%80%93%20crush%20the%20political%20individualism%20of%20Muslim-majority%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20country%20where%20Muslims%20have%20become%20the%20%E2%80%98other%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20verdict%20once%20again%20satisfies%20the%20collective%20consciousness%20of%20the%20same%20political%20majority%20who%20feel%20centuries%20of%20Muslim%20rule%20in%20India%20needs%20to%20be%20avenged%20by%20these%20historic%20corrections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20act%20of%20a%20Muslim-majority%20state%20acceding%20to%20secular%20India%20was%20a%20leap%20of%20faith%20for%20common%20Kashmiris%20and%20crores%20of%20muslims%20in%20India.%20With%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20believing%20that%20president%20of%20India%20can%20unilaterally%20change%20constitutional%20character%20of%20a%20state%2C%20a%20wrong%20precedent%20has%20been%20set%20regarding%20the%20fluidity%20of%20guarantees%20that%20the%20constitution%20of%20India%20provides%2C%20and%20Kashmir%20here%2C%20again%2C%20is%20just%20the%20laboratory%2C%20a%20test%20case%2C%20which%20can%20now%20be%20unleashed%20anywhere%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EToufiq%20Rashid%20is%20a%20journalist%20who%20has%20covered%20the%20Kashmir%20conflict%2C%20health%20and%20wellbeing%20for%20top%20Indian%20newspapers%20for%20nearly%20two%20decades.%20She%20now%20works%20at%20%40Pixstory.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702542920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F10%2F19161014%2FScreenshot-2022-10-19-at-4.10.07-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwhy-there-is-silence-in-kashmir-over-the-supreme-courts-verdict%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court's%20verdict%20shows%20that%20the%20region%20is%20a%20test%20case.%20This%20model%20can%20now%20be%20unleashed%20anywhere%20in%20the%20country.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwhy-there-is-silence-in-kashmir-over-the-supreme-courts-verdict%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Varun's%20film%20with%20dad%20David%20to%20go%20on%20floor%20in%202024%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702542788000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105986344%2Cimgsize-43538.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fvarun-dhawans-fourth-film-with-david-dhawan-to-go-on-floors-in-april-2024-deets-inside%2Farticleshow%2F105986361.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftim