m%20the%20Georgia-based%20Southern%20Association%20of%20Colleges%20and%20Schools%20Commission%20on%20Colleges%20and%20sought%20tax-exempt%20status%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fantoniopequenoiv%2F2023%2F12%2F13%2Felon-musk-university-billionaire-pledges-100-million-to-launch-school-in-texas-report-says%2F%3Fsh%3D1221fc3b106f%5C%22%3Ethe%20%3Cem%3EForbes%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20further%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20doesn't%20provide%20details%20about%20the%20school%2C%20but%20university%20will%20employ%20%26quot%3Bexperienced%20faculty%26quot%3B%20and%20have%20a%20traditional%20curriculum%20backed%20by%20hands-on%20learning%20experiences%20including%20%26quot%3Bsimulations%2C%20case%20studies%2C%20fabrication%2Fdesign%20projects%20and%20labs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Musk%20dumped%20%242.2%20billion%20worth%20of%20Tesla%20stock%20into%20the%20charity%20last%20year.%20The%20proposed%20school%20will%20be%20funded%20through%20tuition%20and%20donations%20and%20offer%20need-based%20scholarships.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20criteria%20for%20student%20selection%20will%20be%20merit%2C%20according%20to%20the%20tax%20filing.%20It%20specifies%20that%20the%20school%20doesn't%20guarantee%20admission%20to%20foundation%20trustees%2C%20officers%2C%20employees%20or%20their%20family%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Musk%20or%20his%20representatives%20have%20not%20responded%20to%20these%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EForbes%3C%2Fem%3E%20said%20Mr%20Musk's%20net%20worth%20is%20%24243.5%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20earlier%20showed%20interest%20in%20launching%20a%20school%20and%20even%20started%20a%20small%20private%20school%20called%20Ad%20Astra%20for%20his%20five%20children%20and%20that%20of%20some%20SpaceX%20employees%20in%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Musk%20had%20clarified%20in%202015%20that%20Ad%20Astra%20doesn't%20have%20any%20grades%20and%20focuses%20on%20%26quot%3Baptitudes%20and%20abilities%26quot%3B%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tech%20billionaire%20has%20also%20shown%20interest%20in%20starting%20a%20new%20community%20called%20Snailbrook%20near%20Austin%2C%20one%20that%20will%20feature%20a%20school%2C%20recreational%20facilities%20and%20subsidised%20housing%20for%20employees%20of%20Tesla%2C%20SpaceX%20and%20the%20Boring%20Company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Felon-musk-texas-town-52386513%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20in%20a%20report%20earlier%20this%20year%20that%20Mr%20Musk%20owns%20around%206%2C000%20acres%20in%20the%20Austin%20area.%20The%20outlet%20further%20said%20that%20Snailbrook%20is%20under%20construction%20and%20will%20need%20at%20least%20201%20residents%20before%20it%20can%20apply%20to%20incorporate%2C%20noting%20a%20final%20approval%20will%20be%20needed%20from%20a%20county%20judge.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702541100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F4dau661g_elon-musk-reuters_625x300_13_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musk-plans-to-launch-his-own-university-pledges-100-million-report-4671975%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk%20earlier%20showed%20interest%20in%20launching%20a%20school%20and%20even%20started%20a%20small%20private%20school.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musk-plans-to-launch-his-own-university-pledges-100-million-report-4671975%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musk-plans-to-launch-his-own-university-pledges-100-million-report-4671975%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musk-plans-to-launch-his-own-university-pledges-100-million-report-4671975%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Parallax%20Picks%20Up%20Sales%20Rights%20to%20Chi