aos%20in%20the%20House%20yesterday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20police%20sources%2C%20Manoranjan%20has%20revealed%20during%20questioning%20that%20he%20attended%20proceedings%20during%20Budget%20session%20in%20the%20old%20parliament%20building.%20This%20was%20a%20recce%20visit%20to%20understand%20the%20security%20checks%20in%20place.%20During%20this%20visit%2C%20he%20found%20that%20while%20visitors%20to%20parliament%20are%20frisked%20multiple%20times%2C%20their%20shoes%20are%20not%20checked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYesterday%2C%20Manoranjan%20D%20and%20Sagar%20Sharma%20hid%20colour%20smoke%20canisters%20inside%20their%20shoes.%20They%20then%20proceed%20to%20the%20visitors'%20gallery%20with%20passes%20issued%20by%20the%20office%20of%20BJP%20MP%20Pratap%20Simha.%20They%20passed%20the%20security%20checks%20without%20being%20detected.%20Later%2C%20they%20jumped%20from%20the%20visitors'%20gallery%20into%20the%20chamber%20and%20deploying%20the%20colour%20smoke%20before%20being%20overpowered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Mysuru%20MP%20has%20explained%20in%20his%20response%20to%20Speaker%20that%20Manoranjan's%20father%20had%20approached%20him%20for%20a%20visitor's%20pass.%20Notably%2C%20MPs%20often%20arrange%20for%20passes%20for%20residents%20of%20their%20constituency%20so%20that%20they%20can%20come%20and%20see%20how%20parliament%20functions.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20four%20arrested%20in%20this%20connection%20have%20told%20police%20that%20their%20objective%20behind%20the%20move%20was%20to%20highlight%20Manipur%20unrest%2C%20unemployment%20and%20farmers'%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20have%20also%20found%20during%20questioning%20that%20Sagar%20Sharma%20came%20to%20Delhi%20in%20July%20for%20another%20recce%20during%20the%20Monsoon%20session%2C%20the%20sources%20said.%20He%20could%20not%20get%20access%20to%20Parliament%20and%20focused%20on%20the%20security%20arrangements%20outside.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20shocking%20scenes%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20yesterday%20has%20put%20under%20the%20spotlight%20lapses%20in%20parliament's%20security%20and%20the%20serious%20consequences%20they%20may%20have.%20Yesterday%20was%20the%2022nd%20anniversary%20of%20the%202001%20Parliament%20attack%20that%20claimed%20nine%20lives.%20Incidentally%2C%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20Gurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannun%20had%20threatened%20an%20attack%20on%20or%20before%20December%2013.%20Many%20have%20pointed%20out%20how%20the%20security%20apparatus%20could%20not%20prevent%20the%20breach%20despite%20being%20on%20high%20alert.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManoranjan%20and%20Sagar%20Sharma%20have%20been%20arrested%20along%20with%20Neelam%20Azad%20and%20Amol%20Shinde%2C%20who%20used%20coloured%20smoke%20to%20protest%20outside%20Parliament.%20The%20four%20face%20charges%20under%20anti-terror%20law%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%20and%20IPC.%20Another%20accused%2C%20Vicky%20Sharma%2C%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20Rakhi%2C%20have%20been%20detained.%20Accused%20Lalit%20Jha%20fled%20the%20spot%20and%20is%20still%20on%20the%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702540980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fdlhlg0t_manoranjan-d_625x300_14_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmonths-before-parliament-security-breach-accused-on-recce-found-key-security-lapse-4671819%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Months%20before%20he%20jumped%20into%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20chamber%20with%20a%20smoke%20colour%20canister%20in%20hand%2C%20Manoranjan%20D%20from%20Mysuru%20found%20a%20key%20gap%20in%20parliament's%20security%20apparatus%20that%20he%20and%20his%20associate%2C%20Sagar%20Sharma%2C%20exploited%20to%20create%20chaos%20in%20the%20House%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmonths-before-parliament-security-breach-accused-on-recce-found-key-security-lapse-4671819%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2