tailed%20feasibility%20study%20is%20on%20track.%20%E2%80%9COur%20plan%20was%20to%20complete%20the%20aerial%20survey%20and%20mapping%20within%202023%2C%20which%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20achieved%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGeological%20survey%20and%20mapping%2C%20spatial%20technical%20studies%2C%20on-site%20surveying%20and%20mapping%2C%20geological%20survey%2C%20construction%20condition%20studies%2C%20engineering%20studies%2C%20and%20preparation%20of%20the%20feasibility%20study%20report%20are%20other%20tasks%20under%20the%20detailed%20feasibility%20study%2C%20according%20to%20the%20department.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGeological%20survey%20will%20begin%20next%20year%20and%20the%20remaining%20tasks%20are%20expected%20to%20be%20completed%20within%20the%2042-month%20deadline%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Bisural.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20late%20November%2C%20talks%20between%20Nepal%20and%20China%20were%20held%20at%20Xiantao%2C%20China%2C%20to%20review%20the%20progress%20of%20the%20cross-border%20railway%20project.%20%E2%80%9CBoth%20sides%20expressed%20satisfaction%20at%20the%20progress%20in%20the%20feasibility%20study%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bisural%20said.%20Keshav%20Kumar%20Sharma%2C%20secretary%20at%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Physical%20Infrastructure%20and%20Transport%2C%20led%20the%20Nepali%20delegation%20at%20the%20talks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20feasibility%20study%20task%20began%2C%20a%20Chinese%20technical%20team%20representing%20the%20China%20Railway%20First%20Survey%20and%20Design%20Institute%20Group%20visited%20Nepal%20in%20late%20December%20last%20year%20and%20conducted%20a%20reconnaissance%20survey%20of%20the%20railway%20project%2C%20according%20to%20the%20railway%20department.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReconnaissance%20is%20the%20first%20engineering%20survey%20in%20a%20previously%20unsurveyed%20territory%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20project%20implementation.%20The%20detailed%20feasibility%20study%20began%20only%20in%20March%20this%20year%2C%20the%20department%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20been%20several%20years%20since%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20political%20leaders%20started%20selling%20the%20dream%20of%20cross-border%20railways.%20But%20it%20took%20longer%20than%20expected%20even%20to%20start%20the%20survey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20analysts%20consider%20a%20railway%20connecting%20the%20Chinese%20border%20town%20of%20Kerung%20with%20Kathmandu%20as%20an%20effort%20to%20counter%20India%E2%80%99s%20project%20to%20connect%20the%20Nepali%20capital%20with%20a%20cross-border%20Railway%20via%20Raxaul.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Prime%20Minister%20Pushpa%20Kamal%20Dahal%20visited%20India%20in%20late%20May%20and%20early%20June%2C%20the%20Indian%20side%20had%20handed%20over%20a%20draft%20of%20the%20Final%20Location%20Survey%2C%20of%20the%20proposed%20cross-border%20Raxaul-Kathmandu%20railway%20to%20the%20Nepali%20authorities.%20According%20to%20the%20department%20officials%2C%20the%20Final%20Location%20Survey%20is%20also%20a%20type%20of%20detailed%20feasibility%20study.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20talks%20about%20building%20the%20Kerung-Kathmandu%20railway%20began%20earlier%20than%20the%20Raxaul-Kathmandu%20project%2C%20the%20feasibility%20study%20of%20the%20northern%20connection%20began%20much%20later%20because%20of%20Covid-19%20and%20China%E2%80%99s%20strict%20anti-pandemic%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20got%20into%20developing%20railways%20in%20Nepal%20when%20former%20prime%20minister%20KP%20Sharma%20Oli%20visited%20Beijing%20in%20March%202016%20during%20his%20first%20stint%20as%20prime%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20out%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20trade%20blockade%2C%20Nepal%20sought%20to%20develop%20alternative%20transport%20routes%2C%20citing%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20overdependence%20on%20its%20southern%20neighbour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENepal%20and%20China%20then%20had%20agreed%20that%20the%20two%20sides%20would%20exchange%20ideas%20and%20proposals%20on%20constructing%20cross-border%20railways%20and%20railway%20networks%20in%20Nepal%20and%20support%20enterprises%20to%20start%20related%20preparatory%20work%20as%20soon%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chinese%20then%20sent%20their%20technical%20teams%20to%20conduct%20a%20preliminary%20feasibility%20study%20for%20the%20proposed%20railway%20in%20November%202017%20and%20May%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20MoU%20was%20signed%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20on%2021%20June%202018%20on%20the%20Cooperation%20in%20Railway%20Project%20when%20Oli%20visited%20China%20during%20his%20second%20stint%20as%20prime%20minister.%20Recalling%20the%20MoU%2C%20the%20two%20sides%20agreed%20to%20conduct%20the%20feasibility%20study%20as%20outlined%20in%20the%20MoU%20when%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fmprc.gov.cn%2Fmfa_eng%2Fwjdt_665385%2F2649_665393%2F201910%2Ft20191013_679597.html%5C%22%3E%C2%A0visited%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0Nepal%20in%20October%202019.%20The%20study%20would%20lay%20the%20foundation%20for%20the%20cross-border%20railway.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20feasibility%20study%20could%20not%20move%20ahead%20instantly%20because%20of%20the%20Covid-19%20pandemic.%20China%20sent%20its%20technical%20team%20to%20conduct%20a%20reconnaissance%20survey%20in%20December%20last%20year%20and%20another%20team%20early%20this%20year%20for%20the%20feasibility%20study.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20building%20this%20railway%20will%20not%20be%20easy%20from%20both%20technical%20and%20financial%20perspectives%20because%20of%20the%20rough%20terrain%20and%20environmental%20sensitivity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20pre-feasibility%20study%2C%2095%20percent%20of%20the%2073-km%20railway%20network%20will%20need%20tunnelling.%20Its%20construction%20cost%20is%20estimated%20at%20Rs293%20billion%2C%20according%20to%20Bisural.%20There%20are%20also%20concerns%20over%20whether%20the%20project%20is%20financially%20viable%20for%20Nepal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20an%20event%20organised%20on%20Tuesday%20by%20the%20Centre%20for%20Social%20Inclusion%20and%20Federalism%20(CESIF)%2C%20a%20think%20tank%2C%20on%20Nepal-China%20relations%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Pushpa%20Kamal%20Dahal%E2%80%99s%20recent%20visit%20to%20China%2C%20experts%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkathmandupost.com%2Fnational%2F2023%2F12%2F13%2Fnepal-should-choose-roads-over-rail-to-china-experts-say%5C%22%3E%C2%A0stressed%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0the%20need%20to%20focus%20more%20on%20road%20connectivity%20than%20railway%2C%20citing%20the%20geographical%20and%20engineering%20challenges%20associated%20with%20railway%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20minister%20and%20Nepali%20Congress%20leader%20Minendra%20Rijal%20questioned%20the%20very%20rationale%20of%20bringing%20Chinese%20rail%20to%20Kathmandu.%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20will%20we%20export%20to%20China%20and%20what%20will%20we%20import%20from%20Tibet%20through%20the%20railroad%3F%20So%20let%E2%80%99s%20build%20roads%20instead.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EPrithvi%20Man%20Shrestha%20is%20a%20political%20reporter%20for%20%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20Kathmandu%20Post%3Cem%3E%2C%20covering%20the%20governance-related%20issues%20including%20corruption%20and%20irregularities%20in%20the%20government%20machinery.%20Before%20joining%20%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20Kathmandu%20Post%3Cem%3E%20in%202009%2C%20he%20worked%20at%20nepalnews.com%20and%20%3C%2Fem%3ERising%20Nepal%3Cem%3E%20primarily%20covering%20the%20issues%20of%20political%20and%20economic%20affairs%20for%20three%20years.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkathmandupost.com%2Fnational%2F2023%2F12%2F14%2Ffeasibility-study-of-nepal-china-railway-on-track-department-says%5C%22%3Eoriginally%20published%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%3C%2Fem%3E%20The%20Kathmandu%20Post.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702536640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F14120229%2Fantoine-beauvillain-0Kw44El