toring%20business%2C%20BartyED%2C%20in%202016.%20Today%2C%20we've%20grown%20to%20an%2011-person%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20worked%20with%20around%20nine%20families%20at%20the%20start.%20My%20business%20now%20has%20a%20core%20group%20of%20around%2080%20families%20whose%20children%20we%20tutor%20%E2%80%94%20mostly%20in%201%3A1%20settings.%20My%20rate%20for%20lessons%20is%202080%20Hong%20Kong%20dollars%20per%20hour%2C%20or%20around%20%24265.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20clients%20are%20generally%20upper%20middle%20class%20or%20above.%20Many%20are%20what%20could%20be%20described%20as%20%26quot%3BHong%20Kong%20old%20money.%26quot%3B%20There's%20also%20the%20Shanghai%20industrialists%20who%20came%20here%20in%20the%2050s%2C%20and%20the%20new%20money%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20course%20of%20a%20decade%20of%20working%20with%20them%2C%20these%20are%20the%20three%20main%20lessons%20I've%20learned%20about%20their%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20You're%20expected%20to%20be%20available%20whenever%2C%20wherever%20your%20clients%20want%20you%20to%20be%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jerome%20Barty-Taylor%2C%2035%2C%20is%20the%20owner%20of%20a%20private%20education%20company%20in%20Hong%20Kong.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6577fb6f58e7c0c29a2bf71b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJerome%20Barty-Taylor%2C%2035%2C%20is%20the%20owner%20of%20a%20private%20education%20company%20in%20Hong%20Kong.%3Cp%3EBenny%20Pang%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20work%20with%20high%20net%20worth%20individuals%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20it's%20old%20or%20new%20money%20%E2%80%94%20I've%20learned%20not%20to%20be%20ruffled%20by%20how%20different%20their%20expectations%20can%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20expect%20you%20to%20be%20available%20on%20their%20time.%20If%20the%20father%20of%20a%20student%20is%20the%20CEO%20of%20a%20multin