%3EEver%20since%20India%20signed%20the%20Shimla%20agreement%20with%20Pakistan%2C%20New%20Delhi%20has%20refused%20to%20accept%20any%20third-party%E2%80%99s%20role%20in%20Kashmir%2C%20asserting%20that%20it%20is%20solely%20a%20bilateral%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20August%202019%2C%20China%20said%20the%20%E2%80%9Creorganisation%E2%80%9D%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20was%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Farticle-370-india-china-diplomatic-spat-ladakh-kashmir%5C%22%3Eunacceptable%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%2C%20particularly%20the%20separation%20of%20Ladakh%20into%20a%20union%20territory.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20Union%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fwhen-i-talk-about-jk-pok-aksai-chin-are-included-in-it-amit-shah-in-lok-sabha-5881916%2F%5C%22%3Ehome%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%3C%2Fa%3E%20told%20parliament%20that%20both%20Pakistan%20Occupied%20Kashmir%20and%20Aksai%20Chin%20are%20integral%20parts%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20year%20after%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20autonomy%20was%20revoked%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fchina-unsc-kashmir-meeting-india-reject-internal-matters-interfernce%5C%22%3EChina%20convened%20three%20closed%20meetings%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20UN%20Security%20Council%20to%20discuss%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20mid-2020%2C%20Chinese%20troops%20went%20beyond%20the%20traditional%20patrolling%20points%20in%20eastern%20Ladakh%2C%20which%20resulted%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Findian-army-officers-killed-china-galwan-valley%23%3A~%3Atext%3DNew%2520Delhi%253A%2520The%2520Indian%2520Army%2Cof%252015%252F16%2520June%25202020.%5C%22%3Eintense%20hand-to-hand%20fighting%20at%20Galwan%20Valley%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20deaths%20of%2020%20Indian%20soldiers%20and%20at%20least%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fchina-acknowledges-casualties-galwan-clash-india-army%5C%2