%99s%20grandfather%20Shivanna%20started%20a%20small%20hotel%20%E2%80%94%20it%20came%20to%20be%20christened%20as%20%E2%80%98Babu%20Hotel%E2%80%99%20very%20recently%20%E2%80%94%20alongside%20farming%20to%20earn%20an%20additional%20income.%20Later%20on%2C%20his%20father%20took%20charge%20of%20running%20the%20eatery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20a%20graduate%20in%20sociology%2C%20Vatsala%20never%20dreamed%20big%20because%20of%20financial%20hardships%20in%20the%20family.%20So%20he%20chose%20to%20stick%20to%20his%20roots%20and%20continue%20the%20family%20business%2C%20unlike%20many%20of%20his%20peers%20who%20migrated%20to%20the%20nearby%20Bengaluru%20city%20for%20odd%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20absence%20of%20present-day%20%3Cem%3Eidli%3C%2Fem%3E%20makers%2C%20steamers%20and%20containers%2C%20the%2045-year-old%20says%20that%20his%20family%20would%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F309836%2Ffood-history-of-idli-sambar-roots-in-indonesia-south-indian-breakfast%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esteam%20%3Cem%3Eidlis%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20small%20bamboo%20baskets%2C%20known%20as%20%3Cem%3Echiblu%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20Kannada.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVatsala%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CBamboo%20is%20available%20in%20abundance%20in%20our%20village.%20The%20villagers%20make%20and%20sell%20many%20items%20made%20using%20bamboo.%20That%E2%80%99s%20probably%20why%20my%20ancestors%20chose%20to%20utilise%20bamboo%20containers%20to%20make%20idlis%20back%20then.%20Moreover%20using%20bamboo%20makes%20the%20process%20very%20natural.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20the%20unique%20preparation%20method%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFirstly%2C%20we%20pour%20the%20batter%20into%20the%20%3Cem%3Echiblu%3C%2Fem%3Es.%20They%20are%20small%20bowl-shaped%20moulds%20made%20using%20bamboo.%20The%20container%20gives%20the%20batter%20a%20perfect%20idli%20shape.%20We%20then%20place%20these%20small%20bamboo%20bowls%20into%20a%20large%20aluminium%20utensil%20using%20bamboo%20sticks%20for%20support.%20Then%20we%20let%20the%20%3Cem%3Eidlis%3C%2Fem%3E%20slowly%20steam%20over%20firewood.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fplugins%2Fpost.php%3Fhref%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.facebook.com%252Fculinaryjourneybynaveen%252Fposts%252Fpfbid0Jhj3eTm6mx67S7cyYDkhocjFkLTESKhrX8GoMGENaQX7v8skATpaV6z67nfotTyxl%26show_text%3Dtrue%26width%3D500%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22689%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVatsala%20informs%20that%20these%20aluminium%20vessels%20%E2%80%94%20around%20two%20feet%20in%20diameter%20%E2%80%94%20have%20the%20capacity%20to%20cook%2080%20%3Cem%3Eidlis%20%3C%2Fem%3Eat%20a%20time.%20Every%20day%2C%20Vatsala%20and%20his%20team%20of%20six%20helpers%20prepare%20at%20least%20eight%20batches%20of%2080%20%3Cem%3Eidlis%20%3C%2Fem%3Eto%20serve%20their%20now%20ever-growing%20customer%20base.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20makes%20these%20%3Cem%3Eidlis%20%3C%2Fem%3Edistinctive%20from%20other%20cooking%20methods%20is%20their%20rich%20aroma%20and%20flavour.%20Vatsala%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20prepare%20the%20batter%20in%20the%20same%20manner%20as%20others.%20But%20the%20whole%20process%20of%20cooking%20it%20in%20bamboo%20baskets%20on%20firewood%20imparts%20a%20rustic%20aroma%20and%20flavour%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3Eidlis%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20these%20%3Cem%3Echiblu%20idlis%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehave%20attracted%20thousands%20of%20customers%20including%20YouTubers%2C%20Government%20officials%2C%20ministers%2C%20movie%20celebrities%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20popularity%20of%20Babu%20Hotel%20rose%2C%20Vatsala%20says%2C%20several%20other%20restaurants%20have%20cropped%20up%20around%20his%20village%20that%20are%20offering%20%3Cem%3Echiblu%20idlis%3C%2Fem%3E%20using%20the%20same%20technique.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20they%20are%20unable%20to%20attract%20as%20much%20footfall%20as%20we%20do%20because%20the%20making%20of%20these%20%3Cem%3Echiblu%20idlis%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20an%20art.%20Every%20step%20of%20the%20process%20needs%20attention%20to%20detail.%20I%20grew%20up%20watching%20my%20family%20do%20this%2C%20so%20my%20learning%20is%20authentic.%20Otherwise%2C%20it%20is%20a%20cumbersome%20process%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fidli-1-1700832066.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20restaurant%20lures%20up%20to%20500%20customers%20on%20any%20weekday.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fidli-1-1700832066.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fidli-1-1700832066-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fidli-1-1700832066-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fidli-1-1700832066-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fidli-1-1700832066-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334923%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20restaurant%20lures%20up%20to%20500%20customers%20on%20any%20weekday.%20Photo%20credit%3A%20Bhakta%20Vatsala.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20art%20of%20making%20%3Cem%3Eidlis%20%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20this%20traditional%20manner%20is%20slowly%20disappearing%20because%20of%20time-saving%20idli%20makers.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20never%20thought%20of%20switching%20to%20%3Cem%3Eidli%20%3C%2Fem%3Esteamers.%20This%20technique%20is%20all%20we%20know%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%20adding%20that%20they%20have%20been%20practising%20only%20this%20technique%20since%20his%20grandfather%20started.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPriced%20at%20Rs%2010%20a%20piece%2C%20the%20hot%20%3Cem%3Echiblu%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Eidlis%3C%2Fem%3E%20at%20Babu%20Hotel%20are%20served%20with%20generous%20amounts%20of%20homemade%20butter%2C%20%3Cem%3Epalya%20%3C%2Fem%3E(fried%20vegetable%20stew)%20and%20fiery%20chilli%20chutney.%20Other%20than%20the%20popular%20%3Cem%3Eidlis%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20eatery%20also%20offers%20crisp%20ghee%20roast%20%3Cem%3Edosa%3C%2Fem%3Es%20like%20%3Cem%3Etuppa%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Ebene%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3Emasala%20dosa%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Echitranna%20%3C%2Fem%3E(spiced%20rice)%2C%20rice%20%3Cem%3Ebaath%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Epalya%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98We%20might%20close%20the%20eatery%20soon%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20typical%20day%20for%20Vatsala%20starts%20at%205.30%20am%20and%20before%207%20am%2C%20his%20hotel%20is%20up%20and%20running%2C%20ready%20to%20welcome%20their%20customers.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20noon%2C%20we%20soak%20the%20grains%20required%20for%20the%20next%20day%E2%80%99s%20batter.%20They%20need%20to%20soak%20for%20at%20least%20three%20to%20four%20hours.%20By%204%20pm%2C%20we%20grind%20the%20soaked%20grains%2C%20and%20by%20late%20evening%2C%20we%20add%20salt%20to%20the%20batter%2C%20mix%20well%2C%20and%20keep%20it%20for%20fermentation.%20The%20batter%20then%20rises%20enough%20to%20make%20soft%20%3Cem%3Eidlis%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20the%20morning%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22in%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EBabu%20Idli%20hotel%2C%20Halagur.%20Malavalli.%20Mandya.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FKarnataka%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23Karnataka%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsribasavaraju%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40sribasavaraju%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FoBMn1U7RsV%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FoBMn1U7RsV%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20DP%20SATISH%20(%40dp_satish)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdp_satish%2Fstatus%2F1323543096458571776%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%203%2C%202020%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EBabu%20Hotel%20is%20open%20for%20business%20between%207%20am%20and%2011%20am%20every%20day.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20exhaust%20all%20our%20batter%20in%20this%20period.%20It%20takes%20us%20the%20remaining%20day%20to%20prepare%20batter%20for%20the%20next%20day.%20We%20are%20able%20to%20wind%20up%20only%20by%208%20pm%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUntil%20recently%2C%20this%20place%20was%20an%20obscure%20eatery%20located%20in%20a%20nondescript%20hamlet%20with%20a%20loyal%20customer%20base.%20But%20with%20the%20arrival%20of%20YouTubers%20and%20social%20media%20publicity%2C%20Vatsala%20says%2C%20he%20has%20gained%20popularity%20overnight%2C%20so%20much%20so%20that%20he%20might%20have%20to%20shut%20the%20business%20in%20a%20couple%20of%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20earlier%2C%20our%20business%20was%20doing%20well%2C%20but%20with%20the%20internet%2C%20my%20business%20has%20flourished%20more%20than%20we%20imagined%20and%20can%20handle.%20Although%20the%20business%20is%20thriving%20now%2C%20I%20am%20exhausted%20with%20all%20the%20increased%20workload.%20I%20am%20unable%20to%20sustain%20the%20crowd%2C%20and%20I%20intend%20to%20shut%20the%20eatery%20in%20the%20near%20future%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20hiring%20more%20people%2C%20Vatsala%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20only%20have%20two%20village%20families%20comprising%20women%20in%20their%2050s%20who%20help%20me%20to%20grind%20the%20grains.%20They%E2%80%99ve%20been%20with%20us%20for%20the%20past%2015%20to%2020%20years.%20Other%20than%20them%2C%20local%20people%20here%20are%20often%20not%20reliable.%20They%20come%20for%20a%20day%20and%20then%20disappear%20the%20next%20day.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20why%20he%20is%20not%20considering%20expansion%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%2045%20years%20old%2C%20my%20father%20is%20in%20his%2070s%2C%20and%20my%20son%20is%20just%20five!%20Though%20popularity%20has%20come%20to%20our%20business%2C%20the%20timing%20has%20been%20unfortunate.%20It%20is%20becoming%20increasingly%20difficult%20for%20me%20to%20sustain%20this%20very%20hotel%20and%20I%20cannot%2C%20at%20the%20moment%2C%20think%20of%20opening%20any%20other%20branches.%20In%20fact%2C%20now%20I%20am%20scared%20of%20the%20social%20media%20reach%20because%20my%20only%20hope%20to%20keep%20this%20place%20up%20is%20if%20I%20get%20reliable%20employees%20or%20volunteers%20to%20share%20the%20load.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Vatsala%20feels%20fulfilled%20looking%20back%20at%20a%20life%20of%20service%2C%20hard%20work%2C%20and%20dedication%20to%20his%20family%20and%20business.%20He%20finds%20joy%20in%20having%20transformed%20his%20family%E2%80%99s%20business%20into%20a%20lasting%20legacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIf%20you%20wish%20to%20help%20Bhakta%20Vatsala%20keep%20%E2%80%98Babu%20Hotel%E2%80%99%20running%2C%20you%20can%20contact%20him%20here%3A%20%2B91%2098863%2075522.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700833878000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fidli-1-1700832066.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D334919%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Located%20in%20Halaguru%20village%20of%20Karnataka%2C%20Babu%20Hotel%20has%20served%20chiblu%20idlis%20made%20in%20bamboo%20baskets%20for%20over%20seven%20decades.%20Its%20owner%20Bhakta%20Vatsala%20shares%20what%20makes%20these%20idlis%20unique.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334919%2Fchiblu-idlis-in-bamboo-beng