india.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fjaswantiben-popat-lijjat-papad-owner-story-1700660151.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D334682%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22From%20Parle-G%20to%20Lijjat%20Papad%2C%20these%20iconic%20food%20businesses%20of%20India%20had%20humble%20beginnings%20and%20inspiring%20stories%20that%20led%20to%20their%20success%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334682%2Flegacy-food-businesses-nilon-parle-g-balaji-wafers-ravalgaon-multicrore%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22When%20Droughts%20Led%20to%20Losses%2C%20Oyster%20Pearl%20Farming%20Helped%20Marathwada%20Farmers%20Reap%20Huge%20Profits%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWith%20uncertain%20rainfall%20patterns%20and%20irrigation%20canals%20completely%20drying%20up%2C%20cultivation%20in%20the%20parched%20land%20of%20the%20Osmanabad%20district%20has%20become%20exhausting%20for%20farmers.%20Lying%20under%20the%20rain%20shadow%20region%20of%20Marathwada%2C%20the%20district%20faces%20acute%20water%20scarcity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrowing%20input%20costs%20and%20unfair%20market%20prices%20have%20severely%20affected%20the%20output%20and%20yield%20of%20the%20major%20crops%20of%20the%20region%20%E2%80%94%20like%20soybean%2C%20sugarcane%2C%20sorghum%2C%20and%20millet.%20The%20compounding%20debts%20put%20Maharashtra%20farmers%20under%20a%20huge%20economic%20burden.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESadly%2C%20the%20recurring%20droughts%20force%20farmers%20to%20sometimes%20end%20their%20lives.%20The%20government%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3ENational%20Crime%20Records%20Bureau%20(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fncrb.gov.in%2Fuploads%2Fnationalcrimerecordsbureau%2Fpost%2F169599016203ADSI-2021Chapter-2Suicides-ExcludingFarmerCauses.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENCRB%3C%2Fa%3E)%20data%3C%2